## PLATO Endpoints

### Base URL
- **URL:** http://147.224.38.131:8847
- **Status:** Running as of 2026-04-28

### API Endpoints
- `GET /rooms` ‚Äî List all rooms (1141 rooms, 10,796+ tiles)
- `GET /room/{id}` ‚Äî Get room data
- `POST /room/{id}/tile` ‚Äî Submit tile (NOT WIRED)
- `GET /stats` ‚Äî PLATO statistics

### Prefix Filtering (Room Discovery)
- `?prefix=forgemaster` ‚Äî Find my work
- `?prefix=fleet` ‚Äî Find fleet coordination
- `?prefix=session` ‚Äî Find session tracking
- `?prefix={domain}` ‚Äî Find domain-specific knowledge

